---
title: Thai Style Yellow Cod Curry With Spinach & Jasmine Rice
description: They grow a lot of coconuts in Indonesia and love to cook with them. The country's food is often spicy but the heat is offset with sweetness from the coconuts and often a sour note too. We're attempting this balancing act in today's curry. The sauce bathing the veggies should be hot, sharp and sweet. Top it all off with golden toasted cashews and the herbal notes of coriander.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/thai-style-yellow-cod-curry-1ebe9d3f-ee0829c6.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/thai-style-yellow-cod-curry-5f3cf5a1b641f71ef95eed6b-f4159443.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/thai-style-yellow-cod-curry-5f3cf5a1b641f71ef95eed6b
author: Michael Steadman
course: main course
time required: 25 minutes
cuisine: Thai
